 Straight from the biggest closing parties of this years Ibiza season comes this Balearic compilation featuring some of the hottest tunes of the island.
 The majority of tunes are hard to categorize, as the Balearic sound might go into Deep House, Progressive but also Trance.
 The album features tunes by the likes of Tiesto, Roger Shah, Sunlounger, LTN, Soundlift, Solis & Truby amongst others. Including a nonstop bonus DJ Mix by Pedro Del Mar.
